Welcome to the Temperature Converter repository! This simple application allows you to convert temperatures between Celsius, Fahrenheit, and Kelvin. Whether you're a student learning about temperature scales or just need a quick tool for everyday use, this converter has got you covered.

Features:
Convert temperatures between Celsius, Fahrenheit, and Kelvin.
Easy-to-use interface with clear input and output fields.
Instantaneous conversion results for quick reference.


Enter the Temperature: Input the temperature value in the provided field and select the original temperature scale (Celsius, Fahrenheit, or Kelvin).

View the Conversion: The converted temperatures will be displayed instantly in the other two temperature scales.

Technologies Used:
HTML
CSS
JavaScript
